56
00:03:40,163 --> 00:03:42,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I woke up this morning...</b></font>

57
00:03:43,243 --> 00:03:44,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Look.</b></font>

58
00:03:44,203 --> 00:03:45,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My face is bruised and it's swollen.</b></font>

59
00:03:46,283 --> 00:03:47,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My whole body hurts.</b></font>

60
00:03:48,523 --> 00:03:49,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What happened last night?</b></font>

61
