192
00:10:55,203 --> 00:10:57,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I passed my exam earlier, okay?</b></font>

193
00:10:58,203 --> 00:10:59,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's all because of me.</b></font>

194
00:11:01,163 --> 00:11:03,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Have you forgotten
who sacrificed sleeping at night</b></font>

195
00:11:03,843 --> 00:11:06,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-and helped you study?
-Never mind. Let's just go.</b></font>

196
00:11:06,083 --> 00:11:07,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

197
00:11:09,363 --> 00:11:10,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

198
00:11:10,563 --> 00:11:11,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

199
00:11:12,123 --> 00:11:14,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But didn't I also help you
with social anthropology</b></font>

200
00:11:14,283 --> 00:11:15,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and sales and marketing?</b></font>

201
00:11:16,003 --> 00:11:17,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wanted to thank you for it.</b></font>

202
00:11:17,563 --> 00:11:21,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But you came and blamed me
about posting our relationship status.</b></font>

203
00:11:24,363 --> 00:11:25,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

204
00:11:25,483 --> 00:11:27,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If apologies worked,
why would we need the police?</b></font>

205
00:11:29,723 --> 00:11:30,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then what do you want?</b></font>

206
00:11:31,283 --> 00:11:32,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Go on a date with me.</b></font>

207
00:11:36,163 --> 00:11:38,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you laughing?
Do you want to come along?</b></font>

208
00:11:52,923 --> 00:11:53,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si.</b></font>

209
00:11:55,403 --> 00:11:57,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where do you want to go
after you graduate?</b></font>

210
00:11:59,203 --> 00:12:01,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought you didn't care.</b></font>

211
00:12:03,403 --> 00:12:04,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After I graduate,</b></font>

212
00:12:06,043 --> 00:12:07,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll go back to London, I guess.</b></font>

213
00:12:10,843 --> 00:12:12,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Back to London?</b></font>

214
00:12:13,323 --> 00:12:14,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>For a vacation?</b></font>

215
00:12:15,203 --> 00:12:16,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course not.</b></font>

216
00:12:16,483 --> 00:12:17,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll help with my family's business.</b></font>

217
00:12:19,363 --> 00:12:20,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then are you still coming back?</b></font>

218
00:12:24,923 --> 00:12:27,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I don't, would you be sad?</b></font>

219
00:12:27,683 --> 00:12:29,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course.</b></font>

220
00:12:29,803 --> 00:12:32,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Won't it be hard to see you then?</b></font>

221
00:12:34,923 --> 00:12:35,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why don't you</b></font>

222
00:12:37,323 --> 00:12:38,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>beg me?</b></font>

223
00:12:39,123 --> 00:12:41,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Beg me and I'd consider staying
in Shanghai for you.</b></font>

224
00:12:44,043 --> 00:12:44,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Really?</b></font>

225
00:12:45,483 --> 00:12:47,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You'll stay if I beg you?</b></font>

226
00:12:47,923 --> 00:12:49,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Will you beg me or not?</b></font>

227
00:12:49,123 --> 00:12:50,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Will you die if you do that?</b></font>

228
00:12:51,043 --> 00:12:52,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course I won't die.</b></font>

229
00:12:54,163 --> 00:12:56,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But just stay if you want to stay.</b></font>

230
00:12:56,723 --> 00:12:57,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why do I need to beg you?</b></font>

231
00:12:58,723 --> 00:12:59,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You silly girl.</b></font>

232
00:13:00,323 --> 00:13:01,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you so stupid?</b></font>

233
00:13:01,483 --> 00:13:02,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You want me to say everything.</b></font>

234
00:13:03,323 --> 00:13:04,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're stupid.</b></font>

235
00:13:04,883 --> 00:13:06,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you want me to stay?</b></font>

236
00:13:06,923 --> 00:13:07,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should say,</b></font>

237
00:13:09,483 --> 00:13:11,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"Can you not go to London?</b></font>

238
00:13:11,123 --> 00:13:13,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can you go to graduate school
and wait for me to graduate?</b></font>

239
00:13:13,723 --> 00:13:15,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can you stay with me forever
after I graduate?"</b></font>

240
00:13:17,523 --> 00:13:18,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Couldn't you say that?</b></font>

241
00:13:22,803 --> 00:13:24,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Really?</b></font>

242
00:13:25,163 --> 00:13:26,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're going to graduate school here</b></font>

243
00:13:27,363 --> 00:13:28,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>so you can graduate with me?</b></font>

244
00:13:31,123 --> 00:13:32,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si.</b></font>

245
00:13:32,243 --> 00:13:33,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

246
00:13:34,283 --> 00:13:35,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm so happy!</b></font>

247
00:13:37,803 --> 00:13:39,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Seeing you smile so cheerfully,</b></font>

248
00:13:39,563 --> 00:13:41,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm so happy too!</b></font>

249
00:13:44,603 --> 00:13:45,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How silly.</b></font>

250
00:14:01,803 --> 00:14:03,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

251
00:14:06,523 --> 00:14:07,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm waiting for you.</b></font>

252
00:14:08,763 --> 00:14:09,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>For me?</b></font>

253
00:14:11,483 --> 00:14:12,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're free, right?</b></font>

254
00:14:15,003 --> 00:14:16,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not.</b></font>

255
00:14:17,283 --> 00:14:19,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have a date with Meizuo.</b></font>

256
00:14:20,043 --> 00:14:20,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A date?</b></font>

257
00:14:21,523 --> 00:14:23,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then why are you coming home?</b></font>

258
00:14:24,763 --> 00:14:26,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I left earlier.</b></font>

259
00:14:26,643 --> 00:14:28,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I realized I forgot something.</b></font>

260
00:14:28,563 --> 00:14:30,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So I came back.</b></font>

261
00:14:31,643 --> 00:14:32,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I'm leaving now.</b></font>

262
00:14:34,283 --> 00:14:35,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not the police.</b></font>

263
00:14:35,363 --> 00:14:36,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not interrogating you.</b></font>

264
00:14:36,563 --> 00:14:38,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why give such a detailed explanation?</b></font>

265
00:14:39,243 --> 00:14:41,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I...</b></font>

266
00:14:42,003 --> 00:14:43,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to tell you something.</b></font>

267
00:14:45,763 --> 00:14:47,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm in a hurry. Maybe next time.</b></font>

268
00:14:47,523 --> 00:14:48,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Meizuo's waiting for me.</b></font>

269
00:14:48,883 --> 00:14:50,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll drive you.</b></font>

270
00:14:52,123 --> 00:14:53,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But...</b></font>

271
00:14:54,403 --> 00:14:56,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Weren't you in a hurry?</b></font>

272
00:14:57,283 --> 00:14:59,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I know Meizuo too.</b></font>

273
00:15:17,723 --> 00:15:19,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>-Hello?
</i>-Hello? Meizuo.</b></font>

274
00:15:19,643 --> 00:15:20,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where are you?</b></font>

275
00:15:20,843 --> 00:15:21,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>At my friend's house.</b></font>

276
00:15:21,963 --> 00:15:23,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can you come over now?</b></font>

277
00:15:24,123 --> 00:15:25,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I need you.</i></b></font>

278
00:15:26,243 --> 00:15:27,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. Right away.</b></font>

279
00:15:32,963 --> 00:15:35,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Guys, I need to go somewhere.</b></font>

280
00:15:35,763 --> 00:15:36,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We just arrived.</b></font>

281
00:15:37,203 --> 00:15:38,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's the matter?</b></font>

282
00:15:40,443 --> 00:15:41,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's an emergency.</b></font>

283
00:15:44,563 --> 00:15:45,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Have some fruit.</b></font>

284
00:15:47,003 --> 00:15:48,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai's still living here?</b></font>

285
00:15:49,203 --> 00:15:50,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where else should she live?</b></font>

286
00:15:51,563 --> 00:15:55,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I mean, she can handle your mom
and stay here.</b></font>

287
00:15:55,723 --> 00:15:56,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's so brave.</b></font>

288
00:15:57,763 --> 00:15:58,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's true.</b></font>

289
00:15:58,803 --> 00:16:01,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I shiver every time I hear his mom's name.</b></font>

290
00:16:02,323 --> 00:16:03,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is his mom that scary?</b></font>

291
00:16:04,043 --> 00:16:05,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh please.</b></font>

292
00:16:05,363 --> 00:16:07,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because of her,
many of her business rivals</b></font>

293
00:16:07,803 --> 00:16:10,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>went bankrupt and homeless.</b></font>

294
00:16:10,643 --> 00:16:14,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If she dislikes someone,
she'll ruthlessly eliminate him.</b></font>

295
00:16:16,403 --> 00:16:17,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop it.</b></font>

296
00:16:20,323 --> 00:16:22,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You even called her an "old hag."</b></font>

297
00:16:22,563 --> 00:16:23,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I...</b></font>

298
00:16:24,403 --> 00:16:26,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did I say that?</b></font>

299
00:16:27,163 --> 00:16:28,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why don't I remember that?</b></font>

300
00:16:29,563 --> 00:16:30,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We all heard it.</b></font>

301
00:16:34,363 --> 00:16:36,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't think you could bully me
just because I'm young,</b></font>

302
00:16:36,683 --> 00:16:37,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you old hag!</b></font>

303
00:16:39,123 --> 00:16:40,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What did you say?</b></font>

304
00:16:40,563 --> 00:16:41,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Say it again.</b></font>

305
00:16:42,203 --> 00:16:43,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Old hag!</b></font>

306
00:16:44,043 --> 00:16:45,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes, I'm calling you that.</b></font>

307
00:16:46,403 --> 00:16:47,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're not welcome in my world.</b></font>

308
00:16:48,483 --> 00:16:49,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get out.</b></font>

309
00:16:52,683 --> 00:16:54,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I said leave!</b></font>

310
00:17:00,523 --> 00:17:01,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When she comes home</b></font>

311
00:17:01,843 --> 00:17:04,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and discovers that person
is living in her house</b></font>

312
00:17:04,523 --> 00:17:06,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and dating her son,</b></font>

313
00:17:07,123 --> 00:17:08,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>can you guess</b></font>

314
00:17:09,083 --> 00:17:10,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>what she'd do?</b></font>

315
00:17:11,363 --> 00:17:13,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, what's your plan?</b></font>

316
00:17:13,563 --> 00:17:15,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's my mom. What can I do?</b></font>

317
00:17:16,683 --> 00:17:18,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But if she threatens Shancai,</b></font>

318
00:17:18,403 --> 00:17:20,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll stand in front of her
and protect her.</b></font>

319
00:17:23,803 --> 00:17:25,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My mom just comes home a few times a year.</b></font>

320
00:17:26,283 --> 00:17:28,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm sure I'll think of something
before she comes back.</b></font>

321
00:17:44,723 --> 00:17:45,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Meizuo.</b></font>

322
00:17:45,763 --> 00:17:47,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What took you so long?</b></font>

323
00:17:47,443 --> 00:17:49,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Do you miss me that much?
-Listen to me.</b></font>

324
00:17:49,763 --> 00:17:52,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When we walk to the bar there,
we have to pretend to be very sweet.</b></font>

325
00:17:52,483 --> 00:17:55,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then you have to say that we have a date,
but you're late.</b></font>

326
00:17:55,363 --> 00:17:56,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right?</b></font>

327
00:17:56,323 --> 00:17:57,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who should I say that to?</b></font>

328
00:17:57,443 --> 00:17:59,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>To that guy you met before.</b></font>

329
00:17:59,203 --> 00:18:00,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Him again.</b></font>

330
00:18:00,203 --> 00:18:01,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

331
00:18:01,163 --> 00:18:02,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't ask.</b></font>

332
00:18:02,283 --> 00:18:03,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hurry. I'll tell you later.</b></font>

333
00:18:04,483 --> 00:18:05,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

334
00:18:05,803 --> 00:18:07,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm late.</b></font>

335
00:18:07,723 --> 00:18:08,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's fine.</b></font>

336
00:18:11,803 --> 00:18:13,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're even late on dates.</b></font>

337
00:18:13,843 --> 00:18:16,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What a good boyfriend.</b></font>

338
00:18:16,643 --> 00:18:17,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why do you say that?</b></font>

339
00:18:17,923 --> 00:18:19,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I respect girls.</b></font>

340
00:18:19,443 --> 00:18:20,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm never late.</b></font>

341
00:18:21,043 --> 00:18:22,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then why was today an exception?</b></font>

342
00:18:22,483 --> 00:18:23,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because...</b></font>

343
00:18:24,283 --> 00:18:25,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because of me.</b></font>

344
00:18:26,363 --> 00:18:27,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's never late.</b></font>

345
00:18:27,923 --> 00:18:30,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But because he's younger than me,
I don't mind even if he's late.</b></font>

346
00:18:31,203 --> 00:18:32,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right?</b></font>

347
00:18:32,123 --> 00:18:33,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

348
00:18:34,283 --> 00:18:35,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Never mind.</b></font>

349
00:18:35,643 --> 00:18:37,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Since we're here to drink,</b></font>

350
00:18:37,883 --> 00:18:39,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>let's order, okay?</b></font>

351
00:18:39,603 --> 00:18:41,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You can't drink. Don't drink anymore.</b></font>

352
00:18:42,043 --> 00:18:43,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I'll order soda.</b></font>

353
00:18:45,923 --> 00:18:47,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You guys can drink.</b></font>

354
00:18:47,323 --> 00:18:48,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay?</b></font>

355
00:18:49,683 --> 00:18:50,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want something strong.</b></font>

356
00:18:50,923 --> 00:18:51,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can you drink?</b></font>

357
00:18:51,923 --> 00:18:53,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should ask if I've ever gotten drunk.</b></font>

358
00:18:55,483 --> 00:18:57,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What matters is your behavior
after drinking,</b></font>

359
00:18:57,483 --> 00:18:58,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>not the amount you can drink.</b></font>

360
00:19:00,083 --> 00:19:01,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What an immature thing to say.</b></font>

361
00:19:02,283 --> 00:19:04,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's basic etiquette for a man
to behave after drinking.</b></font>

362
00:19:04,483 --> 00:19:05,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why is it even worth mentioning?</b></font>

363
00:19:06,763 --> 00:19:09,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Fine. Since you can drink a lot
and behave very well,</b></font>

364
00:19:10,243 --> 00:19:11,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it's my treat tonight.</b></font>

365
00:19:11,323 --> 00:19:12,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No problem.</b></font>

366
00:19:13,523 --> 00:19:14,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wei Xun.</b></font>

367
00:19:14,523 --> 00:19:15,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

368
00:19:16,483 --> 00:19:19,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please give this gentleman a red dynamite.</b></font>

369
00:19:25,363 --> 00:19:26,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

370
00:19:30,123 --> 00:19:31,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sir.</b></font>

371
00:19:31,883 --> 00:19:34,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here on my date with Caina?</b></font>

372
00:19:35,003 --> 00:19:37,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm here to talk to Caina.</b></font>

373
00:19:39,043 --> 00:19:41,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can't you see that we're on a date?</b></font>

374
00:19:42,163 --> 00:19:43,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Very well.</b></font>

375
00:19:43,643 --> 00:19:46,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll say just it in front of him
rather than behind his back.</b></font>

376
00:19:47,243 --> 00:19:48,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Makes sense. Go ahead.</b></font>

377
00:19:49,203 --> 00:19:50,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to talk about that.</b></font>

378
00:19:50,923 --> 00:19:52,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's talk another time.</b></font>

379
00:19:52,163 --> 00:19:53,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

380
00:19:53,283 --> 00:19:54,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why not today?</b></font>

381
00:19:54,923 --> 00:19:57,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because I don't want
to talk about that now.</b></font>

382
00:19:57,083 --> 00:19:58,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-What is it?
-What is it?</b></font>

383
00:20:00,323 --> 00:20:02,323
