<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

575
00:33:44,723 --> 00:33:46,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I used to think</b></font>

576
00:33:47,363 --> 00:33:50,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that you're a harsh</b></font>

577
00:33:51,083 --> 00:33:53,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and unreasonable old lady.</b></font>

578
00:33:55,443 --> 00:33:56,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I am.</b></font>

579
00:33:58,283 --> 00:34:00,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Look at your ugly face.</b></font>

580
00:34:01,203 --> 00:34:02,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop staring at me.</b></font>

581
00:34:04,043 --> 00:34:05,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't look at you then.</b></font>

582
00:34:15,283 --> 00:34:16,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>By the way, Mrs. Yu.</b></font>

583
00:34:17,563 --> 00:34:19,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How did you end up
at the Daoming household?</b></font>

584
00:34:24,723 --> 00:34:26,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's a long story.</b></font>

585
00:34:29,243 --> 00:34:30,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I was</b></font>

586
00:34:31,523 --> 00:34:33,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>19 years old,</b></font>

587
00:34:36,363 --> 00:34:38,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was living alone</b></font>

588
00:34:40,083 --> 00:34:41,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and I needed to pay off debts.</b></font>

589
00:34:42,963 --> 00:34:44,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was in a difficult situation.</b></font>

590
00:34:45,923 --> 00:34:48,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si's grandpa knew about my situation.</b></font>

591
00:34:48,883 --> 00:34:50,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So he paid off my debts.</b></font>

592
00:34:51,403 --> 00:34:53,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And let me work in the Daoming household.</b></font>

593
00:34:54,923 --> 00:34:56,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My life</b></font>

594
00:34:56,643 --> 00:34:58,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was saved by Si's grandpa.</b></font>

595
00:35:00,323 --> 00:35:02,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So I've decided</b></font>

596
00:35:04,323 --> 00:35:06,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to take care of the Daoming family
my whole life.</b></font>

597
00:35:08,923 --> 00:35:12,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll use my life to repay them.</b></font>

598
00:35:14,403 --> 00:35:15,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Later,</b></font>

599
00:35:16,963 --> 00:35:18,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mr. Daoming,</b></font>

600
00:35:19,083 --> 00:35:20,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si's dad,</b></font>

601
00:35:22,563 --> 00:35:25,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>slowly grew up</b></font>

602
00:35:25,603 --> 00:35:26,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and graduated.</b></font>

603
00:35:27,843 --> 00:35:29,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mrs. Daoming married into the family.</b></font>

604
00:35:31,563 --> 00:35:36,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then Zhuang and Si were born.</b></font>

605
00:35:37,923 --> 00:35:41,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This family was happy for decades.</b></font>

606
00:35:42,963 --> 00:35:45,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What kind of person is Daoming Si's dad?</b></font>

607
00:35:46,843 --> 00:35:48,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mr. Daoming</b></font>

608
00:35:49,243 --> 00:35:50,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was really nice.</b></font>

609
00:35:53,803 --> 00:35:55,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's very smart since he was little.</b></font>

610
00:35:56,883 --> 00:35:58,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>At a young age,</b></font>

611
00:35:58,883 --> 00:36:00,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>he handled the Daoming family's business.</b></font>

612
00:36:01,723 --> 00:36:03,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And he didn't disappoint.</b></font>

613
00:36:03,723 --> 00:36:04,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He works very hard</b></font>

614
00:36:05,563 --> 00:36:06,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>all day and all night.</b></font>

615
00:36:08,003 --> 00:36:11,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I often told him
to take care of his health.</b></font>

616
00:36:12,363 --> 00:36:13,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't wear himself out.</b></font>

617
00:36:14,723 --> 00:36:17,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But he said, "I can't.</b></font>

618
00:36:18,443 --> 00:36:20,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The company's employees
are depending on me.</b></font>

619
00:36:21,523 --> 00:36:23,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can I be lazy?"</b></font>

620
00:36:27,923 --> 00:36:30,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's really an outstanding person.</b></font>

621
00:36:31,123 --> 00:36:33,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Indeed.</b></font>

622
00:36:38,283 --> 00:36:39,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I</b></font>

623
00:36:41,403 --> 00:36:44,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>would have wanted him to slack off a bit</b></font>

624
00:36:46,603 --> 00:36:48,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and worry less.</b></font>

625
00:36:52,603 --> 00:36:54,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think I've heard Daoming Si mention</b></font>

626
00:36:56,763 --> 00:36:59,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that his dad already passed away.</b></font>

627
00:37:05,363 --> 00:37:07,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When Si was in high school,</b></font>

628
00:37:09,003 --> 00:37:10,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>he got liver cancer</b></font>

629
00:37:11,843 --> 00:37:12,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and passed away.</b></font>

630
00:37:14,763 --> 00:37:16,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What happened afterward?</b></font>

631
00:37:19,003 --> 00:37:21,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After Mr. Daoming passed away,</b></font>

632
00:37:24,563 --> 00:37:27,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mrs. Daoming handled the Daoming Group.</b></font>

633
00:37:29,603 --> 00:37:30,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This family</b></font>

634
00:37:33,283 --> 00:37:36,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>changed as a result.</b></font>

635
00:37:38,763 --> 00:37:40,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They weren't happy anymore.</b></font>

636
00:37:43,483 --> 00:37:45,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It slowly became cold.</b></font>

637
00:37:47,563 --> 00:37:48,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Zhuang</b></font>

638
00:37:49,723 --> 00:37:51,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>really grew up</b></font>

639
00:37:52,443 --> 00:37:54,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to be a kind girl indeed.</b></font>

640
00:37:57,563 --> 00:37:59,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But Si's temper</b></font>

641
00:38:00,403 --> 00:38:03,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>cannot be controlled by anyone.</b></font>

642
00:38:09,443 --> 00:38:11,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>When Si was in high school,</i></b></font>

643
00:38:12,963 --> 00:38:16,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>he'd always come home with wounds.</i></b></font>

644
00:38:17,643 --> 00:38:20,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>We only found out
when the school notified us</i></b></font>

645
00:38:21,403 --> 00:38:23,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>that he'd been getting into fights.</i></b></font>

646
00:38:26,763 --> 00:38:29,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Mrs. Daoming was worried,</i></b></font>

647
00:38:31,843 --> 00:38:33,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>but because she was busy with work,</i></b></font>

648
00:38:34,003 --> 00:38:35,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>she didn't have much time.</i></b></font>

649
00:38:36,443 --> 00:38:39,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>So she hired a tutor to discipline him.</i></b></font>

650
00:38:40,243 --> 00:38:42,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, you're home.</b></font>

651
00:38:45,003 --> 00:38:46,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Your face--
-You're so annoying!</b></font>

652
00:38:47,563 --> 00:38:48,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>But it was useless.</i></b></font>

653
00:38:49,523 --> 00:38:53,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>More incidents kept on happening.</i></b></font>

654
00:38:56,923 --> 00:39:00,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I was worried and sad
about what was happening.</i></b></font>

655
00:39:01,163 --> 00:39:03,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I really didn't know what to do.</i></b></font>

656
00:39:10,803 --> 00:39:12,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've always been worried about Si.</b></font>

657
00:39:18,643 --> 00:39:20,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After you came here,</b></font>

658
00:39:21,683 --> 00:39:22,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I realized</b></font>

659
00:39:24,083 --> 00:39:25,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that Si has changed.</b></font>

660
00:39:28,643 --> 00:39:29,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did he?</b></font>

661
00:39:30,523 --> 00:39:32,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I didn't do anything.</b></font>

662
00:39:33,603 --> 00:39:34,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I only...</b></font>

663
00:39:36,083 --> 00:39:37,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Initially, I really hated him.</b></font>

664
00:39:40,203 --> 00:39:42,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Whenever I don't agree with his ways,</b></font>

665
00:39:42,443 --> 00:39:43,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I would beat him up.</b></font>

666
00:39:44,283 --> 00:39:45,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Like this.</b></font>

667
00:39:46,123 --> 00:39:47,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's what I did.</b></font>

668
00:39:48,603 --> 00:39:49,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.</b></font>

669
00:39:51,803 --> 00:39:53,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After Zhuang got married,</b></font>

670
00:39:54,443 --> 00:39:58,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>nobody here would dare to do that to him.</b></font>

671
00:40:01,203 --> 00:40:02,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

672
00:40:03,563 --> 00:40:07,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The first time when I beat him up,
I also risked my life to do it.</b></font>

673
00:40:08,123 --> 00:40:10,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's scary when I think about it now.</b></font>

674
00:40:10,723 --> 00:40:13,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you ask me to beat him up now,
I wouldn't dare.</b></font>

675
00:40:16,803 --> 00:40:17,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

676
00:40:19,003 --> 00:40:21,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You can't leave this house.</b></font>

677
00:40:22,043 --> 00:40:23,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I, Mrs. Yu,</b></font>

678
00:40:23,923 --> 00:40:27,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>would risk my life to protect you.</b></font>

679
00:40:31,643 --> 00:40:33,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How's that possible?</b></font>

680
00:40:34,163 --> 00:40:35,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't worry.</b></font>

681
00:40:36,803 --> 00:40:41,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've got a great plan.</b></font>

682
00:40:43,283 --> 00:40:44,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A plan?</b></font>

683
00:40:47,603 --> 00:40:49,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mrs. Yu, I think it's quite late.</b></font>

684
00:40:49,323 --> 00:40:50,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I'll go ahead.
-You can't go.</b></font>

685
00:40:52,523 --> 00:40:54,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you dare to leave,</b></font>

686
00:40:55,003 --> 00:40:57,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>the next time you see me
would be at my funeral.</b></font>

687
00:41:05,403 --> 00:41:06,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mrs. Yu.</b></font>

688
00:41:07,043 --> 00:41:09,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can you threaten me that way?</b></font>

689
00:41:11,003 --> 00:41:13,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Tell me your plan.</b></font>

690
00:41:17,723 --> 00:41:19,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My plan</b></font>

691
00:41:20,323 --> 00:41:21,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>is called...</b></font>

692
00:41:21,963 --> 00:41:25,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>the act first, report later, undercover,
secret, shotgun wedding plan.</b></font>

693
00:41:27,563 --> 00:41:28,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you understand?</b></font>

694
00:41:31,683 --> 00:41:33,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You spoke too fast.</b></font>

695
00:41:33,523 --> 00:41:34,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I didn't hear you clearly.</b></font>

